<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/graph-browser/rdf/node/validate-action> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "A reusable GitHub Actions composite action that validates any data/ directory. Fetches schemas from graph-browser, runs ajv validation on config, graph, tutorials, and view files. Checks referential integrity: edge endpoints exist, kind references valid, tutorial stops reference real nodes, view edge triples match the catalog, and view tour stops are reachable from view edges." .
