<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/graph-browser/rdf/node/tutorial> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Decoder and types for tutorial JSON files. A Tutorial has stops, each referencing a node ID with a depth and narrative text. Narratives support inline links: [text](node:id) navigates to a graph node, [text](https://url) opens external. Tutorials are loaded on-demand when the user starts a guided tour." .
