<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/graph-browser/rdf/node/schema-config> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "JSON Schema for configuration. Defines title, description, sourceUrl (URI format), and kinds map. Each kind has a label, hex color (#rrggbb), and Cytoscape shape (enum of 10 shapes). The kinds map drives all visual differentiation — node colors, shapes, badges, and filter buttons come from here." .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/graph-browser/rdf/node/schema-config> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#group> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/groups#schemas> .
