<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/graph-browser/rdf/node/purescript> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Strongly-typed functional language that compiles to JavaScript. All application logic is PureScript — types catch errors at compile time, Effects track side effects, and algebraic data types model the domain precisely. JavaScript is only used in FFI wrappers for browser APIs that PureScript cannot access directly." .
