<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/graph-browser/rdf/node/prompt-builder> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Pure functions for assembling LLM prompts. Given a Config, Graph, and selected Node or Edge, produces a markdown-formatted prompt with: element JSON, connected elements, JSON schema URLs, source repo URL, file paths, and PR instructions. The user types their intent; the tool provides all the context. No effects — clipboard is handled by FFI.Clipboard." .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/graph-browser/rdf/node/prompt-builder> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#group> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/groups#features> .
