<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/graph-browser/rdf/node/persist> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "localStorage persistence layer. Saves and restores viewer state (selected node ID, depth, tutorial ID, tutorial step) keyed by graph title. Also persists the repo list globally. Uses Argonaut for JSON serialization. State is saved on every graph render, enabling seamless session recovery." .
