<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/graph-browser/rdf/node/nix-flake> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "The build orchestrator. Produces two outputs: app (Main module with repo manager) and lib (Lib module, standalone viewer). Build process: esbuild bundles npm deps (cytoscape + fcose) into deps.js, spago bundles PureScript into index.js, then they're concatenated. mkSpagoDerivation handles PureScript in the Nix sandbox, importNpmLock handles npm deps." .
