<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/graph-browser/rdf/node/lib-output> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "The embeddable viewer built from the Lib module. No repo management — reads data/ relative to the serving URL. Downstream repos consume it via Nix flake input, copy their data alongside the HTML, and deploy. Used by local-llm-graph, cardano-governance-graph, and any project that wants a self-hosted graph browser." .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/graph-browser/rdf/node/lib-output> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#group> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/groups#outputs> .
