<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/graph-browser/rdf/node/halogen> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "PureScript UI framework used for all components. Functional reactive architecture: components are pure render functions plus action handlers. State updates via H.modify_, async via Aff monad, parent-child communication via slots and outputs. Every UI element in graph-browser is a Halogen component or HTML helper." .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/graph-browser/rdf/node/halogen> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#group> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/groups#external> .
