<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/graph-browser/rdf/node/graph-views> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "View types, decoding, and graph filtering. A View selects a subset of edges by (source, target, label) triples and includes per-view tours. filterByView computes the visible nodes from matched edges and builds a filtered Graph. Enables multiple topic-specific lenses over a shared node/edge catalog." .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/graph-browser/rdf/node/graph-views> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#group> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/groups#graph-core> .
