<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/graph-browser/rdf/node/graph-search> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Full-text search across all graph content. Matches against node labels, descriptions, kinds, and edge labels using case-insensitive substring matching. Returns SearchResult (NodeResult or EdgeResult) with up to 12 results shown in a dropdown. Live search on every keystroke." .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/graph-browser/rdf/node/graph-search> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#group> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/groups#graph-core> .
