<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/graph-browser/rdf/node/graph-decode> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "JSON decoders for graph.json and config.json. Uses Argonaut decode combinators to parse node arrays, edge arrays, kind definitions, and links. Handles optional fields (links array defaults to empty). The bridge between raw JSON responses and typed PureScript records." .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/graph-browser/rdf/node/graph-decode> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#group> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/groups#data-loading> .
