<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/graph-browser/rdf/node/graph-cytoscape> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Converts the internal Graph representation to Cytoscape.js Foreign elements. Maps nodes to {data: {id, label, kind}} and edges to {data: {source, target, label}} arrays. The output format is what FFI.Cytoscape expects for rendering. Also identifies the most-connected node for initial selection." .
