<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/graph-browser/rdf/node/graph-build> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Constructs the indexed Graph from raw decoded data. Takes arrays of nodes and edges, builds a Map of nodes by ID and forward/backward adjacency maps (Map NodeId (Set NodeId)) for efficient neighborhood traversal. The adjacency maps enable O(1) lookup of all connections from any node." .
