<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/graph-browser/rdf/node/ffi-cytoscape> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "JavaScript FFI wrapper for Cytoscape.js. Initializes the graph instance with kind-based styling (colors, shapes from config), registers the fCoSE layout plugin, handles element updates with adaptive layout parameters (edge length, repulsion, node separation scale with graph size). Provides event callbacks for node tap, node hover, and edge hover." .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/graph-browser/rdf/node/ffi-cytoscape> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#group> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/groups#ffi> .
