<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/graph-browser/rdf/node/ffi-crypto> <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/page> <https://github.com/lambdasistemi/graph-browser/blob/main/src/FFI/Crypto.purs> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/graph-browser/rdf/node/ffi-crypto> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "AES-256-GCM encryption via the Web Crypto API. Generates a random key on first use, stores it in localStorage. Encrypts GitHub tokens before storage and decrypts on load. IV is prepended to ciphertext, both base64-encoded. Used by the repo manager for private repo access tokens." .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/graph-browser/rdf/node/ffi-crypto> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#group> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/groups#ffi> .
