<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/graph-browser/rdf/node/ffi-clipboard> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Thin wrapper around navigator.clipboard.writeText. Follows the Effect → Promise → Aff pattern used across all FFI modules. Requires a secure context (HTTPS or localhost). Used by the prompt builder's Copy button." .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/graph-browser/rdf/node/ffi-clipboard> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#group> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/groups#ffi> .
