<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/graph-browser/rdf/node/esbuild> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "JavaScript bundler used for npm dependencies only. Bundles bootstrap.js (which imports cytoscape and cytoscape-fcose) into a single minified IIFE file (~555KB). Runs before spago bundle; the two outputs are concatenated into the final index.js. Chosen for speed — sub-100ms bundling." .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/graph-browser/rdf/node/esbuild> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/terms#group> <https://lambdasistemi.github.io/graph-browser/vocab/groups#build> .
<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/graph-browser/rdf/node/esbuild> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "esbuild" .
