<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/graph-browser/rdf/node/cytoscape-js> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Graph visualization library that powers all rendering. Handles node/edge drawing, layout, pan/zoom, selection, and events. Graph-browser uses the fCoSE (compound spring embedder) layout algorithm with adaptive parameters that scale with graph size. Styles are programmatically set from config.json kind definitions." .
