<https://github.com/lambdasistemi/graph-browser/rdf/node/build-action> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "A reusable GitHub Actions composite action that assembles a deployable graph-browser site from a data/ directory with zero build tools. Downloads the pre-built lib variant from GitHub Pages, copies data alongside it, and generates a view index if views are present. Data repos need only JSON files and this action." .
